OL,3,CMurder investigation underway
OL,4,Cfollowing death of man in Kent
OL,6,FA murder investigation is underway in
OL,7,FKent following death of man in
OL,8,FSheerness.
OL,10,FKent Police said officers were called
OL,11,Fto a disturbance inside a private
OL,12,Fproperty in Alma Road at 4.32pm on
OL,13,FThursday 16 April 2026.
OL,15,FOfficers went to the property and a
OL,16,Fman in his 50s was found with an
OL,17,Finjury consistent with a stab wound.
OL,18,FHe later died.
OL,20,FPolice say his next of kin have been
OL,21,Ftold.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
