OL,3,CMurder investigation underway
OL,4,Cfollowing death of man in Kent
OL,6,FA 32-year-old man and a 34-year-old
OL,7,Fwoman, both from Sheerness, have been
OL,8,Farrested on suspicion of murder and
OL,9,Fare currently in custody.
OL,11,FA cordon remains at the property while
OL,12,Fpolice carry out enquiries.
OL,14,FPolice are urging any witnesses to get
OL,15,Fin touch with them.
OL,17,FResidents with private CCTV and
OL,18,Fmotorists with dashcam are also asked
OL,19,Fto check for relevant footage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
